# Project MD Reconstructor

Also read:
- `../../references/project-template.md`
- `../../references/scanning-rules.md`

Goal:
- create or update `docs/project.md`
- keep the fixed template structure
- fill it from repository evidence
- explicitly document reusable building blocks and extension points so future work reuses existing structures
- prefer evidence-backed statements and mark unclear conclusions as inferred or unknown
